      @Nullable default I cast(@NonNull ISequence<?> sequence)
      Cast the provided sequence to this item type.

      Implements the process described in XPath 3.1 Cast.

      Parameters:
      sequence - the sequence to cast
      Returns:
      the original item if it is already this type, otherwise a new item cast to this type
      Throws:
      InvalidValueForCastFunctionException - if the provided item cannot be cast to this type
      TypeMetapathException - if the sequence contains more than one item
